    {
      "id": "0ieK91D6a86xnxUW_WiXW",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -188.15019877091515,
      "y": 1264.6157270273084,
      "width": 918.8333129882812,
      "height": 59.41290360825941,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "6rO55bf7Pu324Eca7eDUe",
        "JmefQHyqBvzGlqxaDKZUV"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "aw",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1607154370,
      "version": 689,
      "versionNonce": 1875694963,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1779095235763,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Service Principal or User-assigned Managed Identity -- to grant terrafrom access to Azure Subscription\nThe Service Principal or User-asssigned Managed Identity should have the Contributor role to create Azure resources\nFor Multi-zone AZ please refer to the github page",
      "fontSize": 15.843440962202509,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Service Principal or User-assigned Managed Identity -- to grant terrafrom access to Azure Subscription\nThe Service Principal or User-asssigned Managed Identity should have the Contributor role to create Azure resources\nFor Multi-zone AZ please refer to the github page",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "_gAmfPsk1B3Zsp2_wx79C",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -194.0914891317409,
      "y": 1346.209447982651,
      "width": 1248.9372713020125,
      "height": 435.69462646056905,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "6rO55bf7Pu324Eca7eDUe",
        "JmefQHyqBvzGlqxaDKZUV"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "ax",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 2042111810,
      "version": 499,
      "versionNonce": 1156572546,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1779038615942,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Service Principal -- https://github.com/sassoftware/viya4-iac-azure/blob/main/docs/user/AzureHelpTopics.md#how-to-create-a-service-principal-using-the-azure-cli\nlogin to using Azure CLI\n\nlogin using below sample\n# example of an Azure CLI login command\naz login\n[\n  {\n    \"cloudName\": \"AzureCloud\",\n    \"homeTenantId\": \"00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000\",\n    \"id\": \"00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000\",\n    \"isDefault\": true,\n    \"managedByTenants\": [],\n    \"name\": \"Subscription Name\",\n    \"state\": \"Enabled\",\n    \"tenantId\": \"00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000\",\n    \"user\": {\n      \"name\": \"user@example.com\",\n      \"type\": \"user\"\n    }\n  }\n]",
      "fontSize": 15.84344096220251,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Service Principal -- https://github.com/sassoftware/viya4-iac-azure/blob/main/docs/user/AzureHelpTopics.md#how-to-create-a-service-principal-using-the-azure-cli\nlogin to using Azure CLI\n\nlogin using below sample\n# example of an Azure CLI login command\naz login\n[\n  {\n    \"cloudName\": \"AzureCloud\",\n    \"homeTenantId\": \"00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000\",\n    \"id\": \"00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000\",\n    \"isDefault\": true,\n    \"managedByTenants\": [],\n    \"name\": \"Subscription Name\",\n    \"state\": \"Enabled\",\n    \"tenantId\": \"00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000\",\n    \"user\": {\n      \"name\": \"user@example.com\",\n      \"type\": \"user\"\n    }\n  }\n]",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "solOCY1aszYP9rfvQ0VrV",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -199.04256443242934,
      "y": 1806.6594509466618,
      "width": 561.4119050126124,
      "height": 158.4344096220251,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "6rO55bf7Pu324Eca7eDUe",
        "JmefQHyqBvzGlqxaDKZUV"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "ay",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 2094638274,
      "version": 331,
      "versionNonce": 1318839618,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1779038615942,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "How to Set the TF Environment Variables\n# set the tenant ID from a query; validate\nTF_VAR_tenant_id=$(az account show --query 'tenantId' --output tsv)\necho $TF_VAR_tenant_id\n\n# set the subscription ID from a query; validate\nTF_VAR_subscription_id=$(az account show --query 'id' --output tsv)\necho $TF_VAR_subscription_id",
      "fontSize": 15.84344096220251,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "How to Set the TF Environment Variables\n# set the tenant ID from a query; validate\nTF_VAR_tenant_id=$(az account show --query 'tenantId' --output tsv)\necho $TF_VAR_tenant_id\n\n# set the subscription ID from a query; validate\nTF_VAR_subscription_id=$(az account show --query 'id' --output tsv)\necho $TF_VAR_subscription_id",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "W08-G1Q_5z39gqQX2M-PB",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -197.06213431215383,
      "y": 1981.927516591027,
      "width": 1381.7845817904943,
      "height": 118.82580721651884,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "6rO55bf7Pu324Eca7eDUe",
        "JmefQHyqBvzGlqxaDKZUV"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "az",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 2123544862,
      "version": 438,
      "versionNonce": 171044098,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1779038615942,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Creating a Service Principal using Azure CLI\nTF_VAR_client_secret=$(az ad sp create-for-rbac --role \"Contributor\" --scopes=\"/subscriptions/$TF_VAR_subscription_id\" --name http://$USER --query password --output tsv)\nTF_VAR_client_id=$(az ad sp list --display-name http://$USER --query [].appId --output tsv)\n\necho $TF_VAR_client_id\necho $TF_VAR_client_secret",
      "fontSize": 15.84344096220251,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Creating a Service Principal using Azure CLI\nTF_VAR_client_secret=$(az ad sp create-for-rbac --role \"Contributor\" --scopes=\"/subscriptions/$TF_VAR_subscription_id\" --name http://$USER --query password --output tsv)\nTF_VAR_client_id=$(az ad sp list --display-name http://$USER --query [].appId --output tsv)\n\necho $TF_VAR_client_id\necho $TF_VAR_client_secret",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "yodqI5u-Kh3gN8hYIUA9P",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -193.10127407160314,
      "y": 2116.596764769748,
      "width": 570.2525721457143,
      "height": 39.608602405506275,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "6rO55bf7Pu324Eca7eDUe",
        "JmefQHyqBvzGlqxaDKZUV"
